@startuml add_product_category
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor #1a5ad7
  FontColor #0b2147
  FontSize 14
}

|User|
start
:Click "Add New Product Category";

|System|
:Retrieve Available\nProduct Categories;
note right
  Query available inventory
  to determine which
  categories can be added

  Independent of current
  fulfillment cycle, same for all
  fulfillment cycles
end note



|User|
:Select Product Category;
note right
  Example:
  - Electronics > Laptops
  - Apparel > Winter Jackets
  - Home > Kitchen Appliances
end note

|System|
:Create Category Entry;
note right
  Initialize all weeks to 0:
  - Week 1: 0 units, $0
  - Week 2: 0 units, $0
  - ... (all 52 weeks)
end note


stop

@enduml
